import React, { useState, useEffect, useRef } from 'react'; import './App.css'; function App() { const [activeSection, setActiveSection] = useState('home'); const [isMenuOpen, setIsMenuOpen] = useState(false); const [typedText, setTypedText] = useState(''); const [typingIndex, setTypingIndex] = useState(0); const [typingState, setTypingState] = useState('line1'); // 'line1', 'line1_done', 'line2' const sections = useRef({ home: null, about: null, projects: null, skills: null, experience: null, education: null, certifications: null, contact: null }); // Typing animation effect useEffect(() => { let timer; const line1 = "print('Hello World!')"; const line2 = "I am Yashwanth, an AI/ML Engineer."; if (typingState === 'line1' && typingIndex < line1.length) { timer = setTimeout(() => { setTypedText(line1.substring(0, typingIndex + 1)); setTypingIndex(typingIndex + 1); }, 100); } else if (typingState === 'line1' && typingIndex === line1.length) { setTypingState('line1_done'); setTypingIndex(0); timer = setTimeout(() => { setTypingState('line2'); }, 500); // Small delay before the second line appears } else if (typingState === 'line2' && typingIndex < line2.length) { timer = setTimeout(() => { setTypedText(line2.substring(0, typingIndex + 1)); setTypingIndex(typingIndex + 1); }, 50); } return () => clearTimeout(timer); }, [typingIndex, typingState]); useEffect(() => { setupIntersectionObserver(); }, []); const setupIntersectionObserver = () => { const observer = new IntersectionObserver( (entries) => { entries.forEach((entry) => { if (entry.isIntersecting) { setActiveSection(entry.target.id); } }); }, { threshold: 0.5 } ); Object.values(sections.current).forEach(section => { if (section) observer.observe(section); }); }; const scrollToSection = (sectionId) => { sections.current[sectionId]?.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' }); setIsMenuOpen(false); }; // Sample data const profileData = { name: "Yashwanth R", title: "AI & Machine Learning Engineer", bio: "Building intelligent systems that learn and adapt. Passionate about deep learning, computer vision, and creating AI that makes a difference.", email: "yashwanth150204@gmail.com", phone: "+91 9345570940", location: "Coimbatore, India", social: { github: "https://github.com/Yashwanth1524", linkedin: "https://linkedin.com/in/yashwanth1524", twitter: "https://twitter.com/yashwanth" } }; const projects = [ { id: 1, title: "Neural Style Transfer", description: "Real-time style transfer using CNN and TensorFlow", technologies: ["Python", "TensorFlow", "CNN", "Flask"], github: "https://github.com/yashwanth/style-transfer", live: "https://style-transfer-demo.vercel.app" }, { id: 2, title: "Predictive Maintenance System", description: "ML system predicting equipment failures using sensor data", technologies: ["Python", "Scikit-learn", "XGBoost", "IoT"], github: "https://github.com/yashwanth/predictive-maintenance" }, { id: 3, title: "Sentiment Analysis API", description: "Real-time sentiment analysis for social media monitoring", technologies: ["Python", "Transformers", "FastAPI", "Docker"], github: "https://github.com/yashwanth/sentiment-api" } ]; const skills = { "Machine Learning": { description: "Developing and implementing ML algorithms to solve complex problems", items: ["TensorFlow", "PyTorch", "Scikit-learn", "OpenCV"] }, "Deep Learning": { description: "Building neural networks for advanced pattern recognition", items: ["CNN", "RNN", "Transformers", "GANs"] }, "Programming": { description: "Writing efficient and maintainable code across multiple languages", items: ["Python", "Java", "JavaScript"] }, "Web Development": { description: "Creating interactive and responsive web applications", items: ["React", "Node.js", "HTML/CSS", "Firebase"] } }; const experience = [ { company: "University of Malaya", position: "Research Intern - AI for Music Digitization", period: "Jul 2024 - Oct 2024", description: "Developed AI-based Optical Music Recognition system achieving 92% accuracy in digitizing historical musical sheets." } ]; const education = [ { institution: "Coimbatore Institute of Technology", degree: "M.Sc. Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning", period: "2021 - 2026", details: "CGPA: 7.89" } ]; const certifications = [ { title: "Deep Learning Specialization", issuer: "DeepLearning.AI (Coursera)", date: "August 2024", link: "https://www.coursera.org/verify/specialization/DLS" }, { title: "Google Cloud Certified - Associate Cloud Engineer", issuer: "Google", date: "September 2024", link: "https://cloud.google.com/certification/cloud-engineer" }, { title: "IBM Applied AI Professional Certificate", issuer: "IBM (Coursera)", date: "July 2024", link: "https://www.coursera.org/verify/professional-cert/AI" } ]; return (
